{"title":"金沙江情思","authors":["李真"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":8,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"金沙江情思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李真"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金沙江映着高高的雪峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚奔腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"噙着泪花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她向我深深地凝望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昔日的风雨中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她是我的摇篮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金沙江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在她的怀抱中起步、成长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我霜染两鬓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又来到她的身旁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨不蚀的怀念，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤起多少戎马倥偬的联想。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六十年前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走在陡崖小路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸雷般的炮声在催促，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水搅着雨水流淌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草鞋扯断耳纽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饥肠咕咕响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举着火把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走在江边石崖上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，那石鼓渡口的人影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那临江蠕动的火龙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星夜兼程，呼应着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金沙江滔天的波浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤手空拳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走在大山密林中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追兵如饿狼扑食，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纳西族人把隐藏好的小船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撑到我颤抖的身旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我摆渡到人生的新驿站。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻越哈巴雪山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿行荒凉草原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战旗在晨光中飘扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个美好的信念，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我心里飞旋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（本诗作者为红军老战士）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}